      • toString

        public java.lang.String toString()
        Prints out the name, city, owner and rent amount for a property
        Overrides:
        toString in class java.lang.Object
        Returns:
        the string representation of a Property object in the following format: Property Name: propertyName Located in city Belonging to: owner Rent Amount: rentAmount Be sure the last item is the rent amount, preceded by a space.
